{"title":"致船长","authors":["赵恺"],"dates":[{"year":2002,"month":10,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"致船长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赵恺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身材无需巍峨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他得准备起伏和摇撼；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"精神必需巍峨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他得战胜起伏和摇撼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"额角描写岩石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头发描写波浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"衣襟描写篷帆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一轮太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"升起在他的左肩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"降落在他的右肩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一群海鸥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌唱在他的身后，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞翔在他的胸前。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的两只眼睛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一只属于暗礁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一只属于冰山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海水则终生依偎着他，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一粒，一粒，一粒，晶莹成生活的盐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高举两臂仿佛双桅之船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船长以利斧斩断锚链。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无锚之船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开弓没有回头箭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农民耕耘土地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船长耕耘海面。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"磔磔雷电伸出两只手臂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一手摇撼农舍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一手摇撼航船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摇撼不动的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是船长的视线。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲸鲨骇异。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冰山退让，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"波涛震颤："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是船吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正面像直立的城堡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"侧面像横卧的峰峦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"电闪雷鸣中驶进哲学境界——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲲鹏展翅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扶摇而上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"击水九万，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举翼三千……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风平浪静中则是一条美人鱼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美人的胸脯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是饱满的风帆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桅杆在甲板上长成大树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大树上高悬着两颗果实，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗叫作太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗叫作月亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日月用昼夜不息的辉光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给纤绳以引导和慰安。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船长亲近光与热，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他吸烟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那红豆一般忽隐忽现的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是诗的标点。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在航船搏击的海面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳在空中游泳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月亮在水中游泳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌声在爱中游泳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在时间里游泳的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——是思念。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}